location.fullValue: Fairway Isles At Slw Country Club Estates

data.description: Location wins again! This home located at the point of a cul-de-sac backing up to a preserve on a large lot and is ready for your finishing touches. The community offers a vacation feel with manicured yards and sidewalks throughout, manned gated entrance and preserves surrounding with a resort style clubhouse-pool-tennis for enjoyment. This CBS Home has endless potential with soaring vaulted ceilings, 3 beds split floorpan, pocket sliders, large kitchen bar and lots of windows that create lots of natural lighting. 2019 a.c 2022 water heater. Huge screened tiled lanai is accessible from the living and main bedroom and is where relaxation calls backing up against a private preserve. Motivated Seller!
